=head1 DESCRIPTION

Contains information about Amazon Web Services Fargate details
associated with an Amazon ECS cluster.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Issues => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

Runtime coverage issues identified for the resource running on Amazon
Web Services Fargate.


=head2 ManagementType => Str

Indicates how the GuardDuty security agent is managed for this
resource.

=over

=item *

C<AUTO_MANAGED> indicates that GuardDuty deploys and manages updates
for this resource.

=item *

C<DISABLED> indicates that the deployment of the GuardDuty security
agent is disabled for this resource.

=back

The C<MANUAL> status doesn't apply to the Amazon Web Services Fargate
(Amazon ECS only) woprkloads.



